<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 16:09:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴勒斯坦国能在经济上实现生存吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/could-a-palestinian-state-ever-be-economically-viable/0000018d-8357-dfd5-adff-dbf7ce830000</link><description>约旦河西岸和加沙拥有一些资产可以用来建设繁荣的经济，但负债也更大。拜登的计划未能解决这个问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 15:49:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/could-a-palestinian-state-ever-be-economically-viable/0000018d-8357-dfd5-adff-dbf7ce830000</guid></item><item><title>法国为哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击事件受害者举行全球首个悼念仪式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/france-holds-worlds-first-memorial-ceremony-for-victims-of-oct-7-attack/0000018d-840e-df76-a1fd-cfffd4b10000</link><description>42 名法裔以色列遇难者的约 100 名亲属参加了在巴黎举行的活动，总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 宣布“今天有 6800 万法国公民哀悼”。一位悲伤的母亲告诉媒体，“在以色列，我们感觉自己被忽视了，感谢法国，我的女儿不会被忘记”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 15:45:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/france-holds-worlds-first-memorial-ceremony-for-victims-of-oct-7-attack/0000018d-840e-df76-a1fd-cfffd4b10000</guid></item><item><title>“未经证实的指控”：英国第四频道猛烈抨击以色列对近东救济工程处的指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/unproven-allegations-u-k-channel-4-slams-israels-charge-against-unrwa/0000018d-837c-d636-adef-cffe76790000</link><description>针对联合国巴勒斯坦难民救济机构的指控是在一份以色列情报简报中提出的，最初是在《华尔街日报》上报道的。英国第四频道声称“没有证据”证明以色列对近东救济工程处工作人员的指控</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 15:28:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/unproven-allegations-u-k-channel-4-slams-israels-charge-against-unrwa/0000018d-837c-d636-adef-cffe76790000</guid></item><item><title>停火协议将是哈马斯的巨大胜利，但以色列别无选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-cease-fire-deal-would-be-a-huge-victory-for-hamas-but-israel-has-no-choice/0000018d-8346-d361-a9cd-e7ee36500000</link><description>2011 年，我参与谈判的哈马斯与以色列人质协议规定，以 1,000 多名巴勒斯坦囚犯换取一名以色列士兵。这本应该是以色列最后一次不得不赎回其公民，但今天，哈马斯占了上风</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:59:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-cease-fire-deal-would-be-a-huge-victory-for-hamas-but-israel-has-no-choice/0000018d-8346-d361-a9cd-e7ee36500000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质及其家人为内塔尼亚胡和加兰特的吹嘘付出代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-pay-the-price-for-netanyahu-and-gallants-boasting/0000018d-8363-d361-a9cd-e7eb4bec0000</link><description>即使总理和国防部长的目的是削弱哈马斯在谈判中的地位，他们对哈马斯领导人被暗杀的无休止的谈论似乎已经取代了行动</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:56:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-pay-the-price-for-netanyahu-and-gallants-boasting/0000018d-8363-d361-a9cd-e7eb4bec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军预备役军人在加沙战斗中受伤几周后死于真菌感染</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-reservist-dies-of-fungal-infection-weeks-after-suffering-wounds-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-83aa-dfd5-adff-dbbbc75a0000</link><description>在各种治疗未能治愈感染后，这名26岁的男子服用了卫生部批准的特殊用途的实验药物</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:50:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-reservist-dies-of-fungal-infection-weeks-after-suffering-wounds-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-83aa-dfd5-adff-dbbbc75a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列选择欧洲电视网参赛者，呼吁禁止参加加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-selects-eurovision-contestant-amid-calls-to-ban-participation-over-gaza-war/0000018d-832d-dfd5-adff-dbbda1b90000</link><description>20 岁的伊登·戈兰 (Eden Golan) 在赢得以色列歌唱电视节目 HaKokhav Haba 后获得提名，她将面临围绕以色列参加国际歌唱比赛已经存在的争议</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:45:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-selects-eurovision-contestant-amid-calls-to-ban-participation-over-gaza-war/0000018d-832d-dfd5-adff-dbbda1b90000</guid></item><item><title>“胜利在于框架”：六日战争期间大胆的以色列音乐剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/movies/2024-02-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/victory-is-a-matter-of-framing-the-daring-israeli-musical-set-during-the-six-day-war/0000018d-5954-d0fc-a9bd-5f5d002a0000</link><description>一位患有创伤后应激障碍 (PTSD) 的以色列退伍军人偶然发表的评论，让编剧兼导演埃里兰·佩莱德开始了长达七年的冒险之旅。最终的成果是他 1967 年创作的《胜利》，这是一部色彩缤纷但极其复杂的音乐剧，与当今的以色列息息相关</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/movies/2024-02-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/victory-is-a-matter-of-framing-the-daring-israeli-musical-set-during-the-six-day-war/0000018d-5954-d0fc-a9bd-5f5d002a0000</guid></item><item><title>解释者：美国制裁的以色列定居者是谁？他们的目标意味着什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/who-are-the-israeli-settlers-sanctioned-by-the-u-s-and-what-does-their-targeting-mean/0000018d-8233-d636-adef-ceffc2980000</link><description>以色列银行开始封锁犹太定居者的账户，以遵守拜登政府因袭击巴勒斯坦人而对四名以色列定居者实施的制裁。他们是谁？对未来可能产生哪些影响？</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 13:49:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/who-are-the-israeli-settlers-sanctioned-by-the-u-s-and-what-does-their-targeting-mean/0000018d-8233-d636-adef-ceffc2980000</guid></item><item><title>人质仍然是辛瓦尔最有效的杠杆，也是他在谈判中唯一讨价还价的筹码</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/hostages-remain-sinwars-most-effective-lever-and-his-only-bargaining-chip-in-talks/0000018d-82b0-d6dc-ab9f-cffdfb5b0000</link><description>哈马斯在加沙和国外的领导层非常清楚，只有人质问题才能让数以万计的以色列人走上街头，也只有这场斗争才能迫使内塔尼亚胡处理棘手的问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 13:07:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/hostages-remain-sinwars-most-effective-lever-and-his-only-bargaining-chip-in-talks/0000018d-82b0-d6dc-ab9f-cffdfb5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列心理学家阻止下一个摩萨德叛徒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-psychologists-stopping-the-next-mossad-traitor/0000018d-7f37-daa1-a9fd-7f3ff0e80000</link><description>以色列情报部门不仅使用心理分析来分析敌人，还用于筛查和治疗在敌对领土上进行作战活动的人员，因为他们知道他们冒着生命危险</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 12:58:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-psychologists-stopping-the-next-mossad-traitor/0000018d-7f37-daa1-a9fd-7f3ff0e80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的暴雨揭示了古代亚述圣甲虫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-07/ty-article/rainstorm-in-israel-reveals-ancient-assyrian-scarab/0000018d-8358-dfd5-adff-dbf9f16b0000</link><description>圣甲虫印章是用半宝石红玉髓雕刻而成，一侧似乎显示出一只狮鹫，或者可能是一只有翼的四足动物。确定圣甲虫的年代很有挑战性，但它看起来最像公元前八世纪的圣甲虫</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 12:02:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-07/ty-article/rainstorm-in-israel-reveals-ancient-assyrian-scarab/0000018d-8358-dfd5-adff-dbf9f16b0000</guid></item><item><title>“他是犹太人？不，他只是爱以色列”：阿根廷总统在西墙受到英雄般的欢迎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-just-loves-israel-argentine-president-milei-gets-heros-welcome-at-western-wall/0000018d-830e-d636-adef-cfee20ee0000</link><description>周二，极右翼阿根廷领导人哈维尔·米莱（Javier Milei），又名“大头发的家伙”，在他为期三天的以色列之行的第一站吸引了一群喧闹的人群。一位以色列人解释说，“我们需要更多像他这样的人——全世界都在反对我们”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 10:54:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-just-loves-israel-argentine-president-milei-gets-heros-welcome-at-western-wall/0000018d-830e-d636-adef-cfee20ee0000</guid></item><item><title>“难以忍受的过度拥挤”：哈马斯战争期间以色列设施中的囚犯被关在拥挤的牢房里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/intolerable-overcrowding-prisoners-held-in-packed-cells-in-israel-amid-hamas-war/0000018d-8231-d6dc-ab9f-cf7de6820000</link><description>根据公设辩护人办公室的一份报告，囚犯遭受“卫生条件差、卫生问题和虫害困扰”，大约 3,400 名囚犯睡在地板上的床垫上</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 10:38:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/intolerable-overcrowding-prisoners-held-in-packed-cells-in-israel-amid-hamas-war/0000018d-8231-d6dc-ab9f-cf7de6820000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯提议停火135天、以色列从加沙撤军、谈判结束战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/hamas-proposes-135-day-cease-fire-israeli-withdrawal-from-gaza-talks-to-end-war/0000018d-82b3-d6dc-ab9f-cfffb16f0000</link><description>根据三阶段停火草案，将用人质换取1500名巴勒斯坦囚犯，移交被杀人质的遗体，以军全面撤军</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 10:06:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/hamas-proposes-135-day-cease-fire-israeli-withdrawal-from-gaza-talks-to-end-war/0000018d-82b3-d6dc-ab9f-cfffb16f0000</guid></item><item><title>沙特阿拉伯排除在没有巴勒斯坦国的情况下与以色列建立联系，结束加沙“侵略”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/saudi-arabia-rules-out-diplomatic-ties-with-israel-without-independent-palestinian-state/0000018d-829e-d636-adef-cefefe590000</link><description>就在美国国家安全委员会发言人约翰·柯比表示释放人质和以色列与沙特关系正常化问题是“不同的轨道”的一天后，沙特阿拉伯外交部表示，如果没有巴勒斯坦国，就不会有任何关系</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 09:37:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/saudi-arabia-rules-out-diplomatic-ties-with-israel-without-independent-palestinian-state/0000018d-829e-d636-adef-cefefe590000</guid></item><item><title>在史前波兰发现的青铜珠宝可能是祭祀仪式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-07/ty-article/bronze-jewels-found-in-prehistoric-poland-may-have-been-ritual-sacrifices/0000018d-7eda-d6dc-ab9f-7fffac880000</link><description>人们认为欧洲青铜时代的海乌姆诺文化不使用金属。但新的研究认为，古代湖床上的青铜首饰可能是代替人类提供的</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-07/ty-article/bronze-jewels-found-in-prehistoric-poland-may-have-been-ritual-sacrifices/0000018d-7eda-d6dc-ab9f-7fffac880000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部城市卡夫卡塞姆的一名男子在家中被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-his-home-in-central-israeli-city-of-kafr-qasem/0000018d-8230-d6dc-ab9f-cf7de0bc0000</link><description>以色列阿拉伯社区凶杀率急剧上升，48 岁男子在家中被谋杀</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:17:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-his-home-in-central-israeli-city-of-kafr-qasem/0000018d-8230-d6dc-ab9f-cf7de0bc0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡为了空洞的口号和政治利益牺牲了加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sacrificed-the-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-for-empty-slogans-and-political-gain/0000018d-8047-d636-adef-ceef8b310000</link><description>《纽约时报》有关仍被哈马斯俘虏的以色列人命运的报道对于政界或军事界的任何人来说都不足为奇。家人声称“时间不多了”的说法如今听起来截然不同</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:02:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sacrificed-the-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-for-empty-slogans-and-political-gain/0000018d-8047-d636-adef-ceef8b310000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡拒绝调解努力，人质家属加大力度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-to-intensify-their-campaign-as-netanyahu-rebuffs-mediation-efforts/0000018d-8003-daa1-a9fd-e20baf6b0000</link><description>哈马斯再次要求结束战争作为达成任何协议的条件，而内塔尼亚胡部分出于政治原因表示反对。即使达成临时协议似乎也还有很长的路要走 ■ 有报道称，在囚禁期间死亡的人质人数比以色列承认的还要多，政府似乎对战争失去了兴趣</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:01:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-to-intensify-their-campaign-as-netanyahu-rebuffs-mediation-efforts/0000018d-8003-daa1-a9fd-e20baf6b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>